{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a688c59264","title":"关于欢迎出席新政协会议致程潜电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ce93691663","index":0,"year":1949,"month":8,"day":30,"articleId":"a688c59264"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"24a5404620","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"a688c59264","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"程潜，原任国民党湖南省政府主席、国民党军长沙绥靖公署主任。1949年8月4日在长沙宣布起义，湖南和平解放。"},{"id":"6df16fc8c7","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"a688c59264","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈子良，即陈明仁，号子良，原任国民党军第一兵团司令官，1949年8月4日与程潜一起在长沙宣布起义。"},{"id":"2741858e14","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"a688c59264","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"未皓，即8月19日。"},{"id":"b439d7ec67","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"a688c59264","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"优亦山，即优整，原任国民党政府湖南省政府委员，1949年参加湖南和平解放工作。"}],"contents":[{"id":"c214a8220e","type":"title","text":"关于欢迎出席新政协会议致程潜“电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"a688c59264"},{"id":"24a5404620","type":"paragraph","text":"长沙程颂云先生：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"a688c59264"},{"id":"6df16fc8c7","type":"paragraph","text":"八月十九日电示今日收到，敬悉。尊见极好，完全同意。当接陈子良以兄未皓电时，我即复电（经中共湖南省委转）请他仍照前议兼领省主席，与尊意吻合。新政协召开在即，拟请我公及优办山、陈子良出席，共商国是，他能命驾，无任欢迎。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"a688c59264"},{"id":"2741858e14","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"a688c59264"},{"id":"b439d7ec67","type":"paragraph","text":"未州","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"a688c59264"}],"page":{"id":"8bb2106b51","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"a688c59264","start":197,"end":197}}}},"__N_SSG":true}